# Personal deck files (mutable user state managed by the sidecar). The
# placeholder .gitkeep is kept so the directory still exists on a fresh
# clone — without it, the sidecar's deck loader has nowhere to scan.
# Revisit if/when we want decks versioned alongside cards.
data/decks/*
!data/decks/.gitkeep
